title: Execution of an executable in an VFS-Local-Encryption on Windows (10/64Bit)
body:

I cannot execute an executable under Windows 10/64 Bit, like an install exe.
VFS
Local-Filesystem
Encrypted
Mounted as a Folder

1.45 (Beta but also the stable)


#### Which OS you are using and how many bits (eg Windows 7, 64 bit)
Windows 10/64Bit


####  Which cloud storage system are you using? (eg Google Drive)
Local-Filesystem
